('134076296', 'applestore', 'United States', 'New version is terrible', 'I use this every day. Not for the traffic, but for the reporting of accidents and speed traps, and to contribute my speed info. I use it so often that I am at royalty level. Has saved us time on quite a few occasions by detouring around traffic on longer road trips.\n\nHowever... Version 4 brought a redesign and with it came bugs. Some buttons are now too small, and require more focus to tap while driving. Often I am given a map with not a single street name on it for miles. Also, now I can\'t report any road hazards or traffic conditions on the other side of the road. Accidents and cops still work, but any other report has no \"other side\" option. So stupid to have left that out. Also when reporting police you can\'t do other side AND hidden/visible. Could always do this in the old version.\n\nWhen waze brings back the ability to report things on the other side of the road, I will increase my rating. Until then, 1 star.', '105747713', 'applestore', 'France', 'Very good', 'I find Waze very well done. I only put 3 stars because months ago a red dot appears showing me 8 messages that I could never read. It is not because I have an iPhone 4 that I should no longer have access to this function. Otherwise super', 'Waze', 0.0673581, 2, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 34, -2, 2, 0.5, 'ot', 'ot'),
