('152349360', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Sound issue this update', 'Have used this app for a few years.  Generally happy with the app, navigation, features.  However, this update has an issue.  If you are NOT bluetoothed, any navigation sounds are whispers.  Checked the sound settings on the app, all is on/normal/high.  Other apps play normal volume through phone speaker.  (This app used to as well.). Now only plays normal volume when bluetoothed.\n\nAs an aside, it really would be great to have an alert for pedestrian on highway.  The closest that comes to it is \"animal on road\".  \n\nI use this app whenever I drive, even though I have a built in nav system in my car.  It really is my go-to nav app.  Please fix this sound issue.', '147845760', 'applestore', 'France', 'Bug on sound', 'Since the update made yesterday the sound is inaudible on the application! It becomes difficult to guide oneself!', 'Waze', 0.20546, 2, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 40, 2, -2, 0.5, 'br', 'ot'),
