('341469115', 'applestore', 'United States', 'I use this app all the time, but...', 'Spotify is basically the only app I ever use, but there\'s one thing in particular about the latest version that\'s really bothering me; when I make a playlist, I can\'t see who\'s following it.. As a user, I\'d like to see who\'s listening to my playlists, so.. yeah. I don\'t like that, but otherwise I love it!', '274071630', 'applestore', 'France', 'Spotify et Sonos', 'Forcing Sonos speaker users to have a premium account just makes me uninstall Spotify. You have to correct that.', 'Spotify', 0.0562328, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 150, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('34281878', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Good concept, but needs improvement', 'This app is great to just have open if you have a dash mount for your iPhone. It\'s best feature is the way it shows you the \"fastest\" route (still deciding if that\'s true).\nIMPROVEMENT IDEA: I\'d like to only be alerted for \"lurking\" police, that is police that have their radar pointed at the road. I think most people would agree. As it is, I also get alerts for police that have pulled others over and have blinkers on and *gasp* cars on the shoulder. Most of us can see these things easily and do not need spoken alerts for them.\nAnother minor qualm I have is that when I open the app, it often begins me on a route that it \"thinks\" I want. I almost never do and need to go on and close it. Please fix!', '530080415', 'applestore', 'France', 'Super!!!!!!', 'Better and better Superb application However the Waze are a bit small', 'Waze', 0.0302798, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 151, 1, 3, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
('349550545', 'applestore', 'United States', 'GPS usage', 'I think waze eats up battery as it uses GPS all time even when not used. It would be great if we have option to choose to use GPS when app is actually used.', '163209485', 'applestore', 'France', 'I recommend', 'Very well, both alert and GPS.', 'Waze', 0.0821528, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 152, 2, 0, 0.75, 'fr', 'ot'),
