('37070883', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great music app but too many BT issues', 'I don\'t know what it is with this app but I\'m starting to lose my patience with the Bluetooth issues. Most of the time I have to force close the app in my car to get it to play through. Now, most of the time I\'m having trouble with Bluetooth playing on my Bose speaker. I think it\'s iOS. Why do I need to turn up the volume full blast on the iphone/ipad and Bose?', '133315165', 'applestore', 'France', 'Super but takes up space', 'Spotify has become my only source of music. I use it in premium mode (included in my phone subscription). Most of the time, I listen to it in 4g / wifi, but the offline mode is very convenient on the move. Playlists are varied and good. The radio mode, which allows to listen to songs &quot;similar&quot; to a given piece, is very good because it follows my desires of the moment. Only problem (which costs a star), the space occupied by the app increases very quickly, even without downloading many songs, without my understanding why. Unable to &quot;clean&quot; the app data. Only solution I found, remove regularly and reinstall the app.', 'Spotify', 0.207969, 0, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 171, 1, 1, 1, 'br', 'ot'),
('37257488', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Was Great', 'The app is always using mummy location. There needs to be an option in the next release to use location while app is open.', '110590214', 'applestore', 'France', 'Good but', 'Very good GPS application. Complete and intuitive, it will delight motorists. The only major complaint is the almost permanent activation of the location even if the application is not open. As a result, the battery discharges much faster. The other apps offer a mode where the GPS is active only when the application is open like Google Maps or Apple Plan ...', 'Waze', 0.201336, 2, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 172, 0, 1, 0.875, 'br', 'ot'),
('37565749', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Please Get an iWatch App', 'This is a great app, and I love it. But please please please make an Apple Watch app and I\'ll write you a great review again! :)', '362775528', 'applestore', 'France', 'Great app', 'Great app but it\'s a shame it does not exist on Apple Watch! Please make it in one!', 'Waze', 0.453841, 4, 2, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 173, 3, 1, 0.75, 'fr', 'ot'),
('38000177', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Wonderful with a few bugs!', 'I once loved this app and used it over my nav system in my car because it always seems to know the shortest route to my destination - throughout the country! But no more! The current version often has connection problems and often freezes in the middle of my trip and I loose sound instructions. Not sure why this happens and it is unsafe. Also I have one location on a highway I am frequently on where the app seems to lose its way and gives crazy instructions. All that being said, I liked this app to hope that they will get this fixed. For now, it is now not my preferred gps app.', '224637340', 'applestore', 'France', 'Great app', 'Very satisfied with this free gps!', 'Waze', 0.108042, 0, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 174, 3, 3, 1, 'ot', 'br'),
('38099926', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great app!', 'One of the best apps of all time. It gets better with each update. Lane assist would be great. Let\'s keep building on the success.\nGreat Job!!!', '460288267', 'applestore', 'France', 'Discovery tour', 'I join this Pleiades of praises. The shortcuts are sometimes very amazing! This makes the paths and contours of bottling more friendly, less monotonous? Will the application take into account the characteristics of vehicles (trucks, 2 motorcycles, cycle or basket)? To further optimize the journeys of each one. Good route to all the Wazers.', 'Waze', 0.124781, 2, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 175, 3, 3, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
