('115427958', 'applestore', 'United States', 'It USED to be awesome, now, not so much', 'I used to rely on Waze heavily to navigate me through traffic, but lately it\'s been taking me off a decent route and putting me into gridlock. And it constantly has me do idiotic things like take a freeway exit only to get right back on. AND it eats through your battery even if you have the program closed down because it is ALWAYS using your location... there is no \"while using the app\" option. I\'M DONE!!!', '78034301', 'applestore', 'France', 'Permanent Location &amp; Big Battery Console', 'Even when the application is turned off Waze uses your location data. No possibility to activate the location in mode &quot;when the app is active&quot;. So locating and exchanging permanent data: it eats the battery and I do not want to be tracked down.', 'Waze', 0.214182, 2, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 367, 0, 0, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
('11633952', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great!!!!!', 'Great app, access to a lot of music; impressive what one finds with the search function.  At times a bit complicated to use, but that could be because i use it in my iPhone, Sonos and Tap systems and they are linked.  Listening to more music than in a long time.', '274071630', 'applestore', 'France', 'Spotify et Sonos', 'Forcing Sonos speaker users to have a premium account just makes me uninstall Spotify. You have to correct that.', 'Spotify', 0.150137, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 368, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
