('117604359', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Using GPS in the background and draining the battery', 'Love the navigation and use all the time, but finally got enough, after realizing it\'s Waze and only Waze which made my iPhone 6S Plus not last through the day, like in the old days. The GPS icon is always on, and the choice in the Settings for the GPS is either \"never\" or \"always\". They should have \"while using the app\" option or at least make Waze stop using the GPS ALL the time!! Closing the app and removing Waze widget didn\'t help. So I will have to delete this app till it\'s better, sadly....', '152628622', 'applestore', 'France', 'Super', 'I use it on a daily basis for all my journeys from the shortest to the longest?', 'Waze', 0.13996, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 370, 0, 2, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
