('129464675', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great', 'Very helpful as we travel across the country.\n\nOne upgrade would be great for us who live in States with Frontage roads:\nSince the app knows the traffic density on the frontage road, use this information for making a right turn, to have you exit one exit earlier to give sufficient time to get into the lane for the turn. Currently you exit and then have to cross 3 lanes of heavy traffic in 1000ft to make your turn.', '4080', 'applestore', 'France', 'Top', 'I am very pleased with my change between coyote and Waze. I use it on a daily basis', 'Waze', 0.0379566, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 378, 1, 2, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
