('152204172', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Skip this update', 'This update will give you problems. The sound prompts don\'t come out the speaker, but the handset speaker. The only way to hear it is to put the iPhone up to your head.', '167281898', 'applestore', 'France', 'Big problem of sound !!', 'Hello, since the last update, there is no longer the possibility to select Bluetooth automatically. Either it is forced in call mode but in this case, the sound of the application is diffused in the loudspeaker of the telephone (where one hears the speaker and more in the conventional loudspeaker), or One chooses to force to diffuse in the conventional loudspeaker but it no longer works in Bluetooth. Why did you touch something that worked properly ??? I hope this problem will be solved soon because it is really painful every time to make the change of parameters before each course !!', 'Waze', 0.221642, 3, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 390, -1, -2, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
