('152971608', 'applestore', 'United States', 'FIX Planned Drives please', 'Ever since 4.0 I don\'t get notifications of when is time to leave like it used to when it was a calendar feature only. I\'m tired of testing the app every time a new version comes up. I NEVER get notifications from ANY device in Puerto Rico. If it worked before 4.0 why not now, there has to be something in the code dragging version by version after 4.0 that\'s impeding this, it\'s location based because in Florida only ONCE worked. C\'mom guys don\'t offer a feature that simply doesn\'t work! I relied on this so much!!!', '106974146', 'applestore', 'France', 'Finally!!!', 'Finally an effective app to predict its movements, or manage them in progress! I do not mind', 'Waze', 0.0300921, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 392, 0, 1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
