('155650926', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Go Netflix!!', 'Netflix is on top of their game. I\'ve had Netflix for years now and over the years they have gotten app much better. New contents every month. #1 streaming app. This new download and watch offline is an incredible idea. Also it\'s free! Ain\'t nobody beating Netflix now. Keep up the good work.', '403789357', 'applestore', 'France', 'Apple Watch', 'Fun application but take out the app for the Apple watch !!!!', 'Spotify', 0.61287, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 396, 1, 1, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
