st shoulder. Anything that is done while driving needs to be simplified. Too many clicks. Also need ability to click anywhere to send a report- does not feature that. Also should be able to tag while on the phone (with Verizon can\'t) and put in info after data connection back. Also what gives. I\'m always told I\'m reporting too much. Well there are always lots of things to report. Just raise that maximum a little.  I might report two cars, one police, traffic and debris all in 1 mile\n\n---', '262337148', 'applestore', 'France', 'Very good application, but lack of little things yet!', 'Police, traffic congestion, speed cameras, hazards ... Everything a driver needs to know! Personally, as well, see better than a GPS sold in supermarkets, more than a year of use, always well warned in case of worries, and always given a good road! I will just add the fact of being able to prevent a danger an accident or other after arriving at our place, but at the stop, because unfortunately if one does not prevent at the moment where it passes to the precise place, Can more ... if not the top!', 'Waze', 0.211996, 1, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 402, -1, -1, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
