('185630015', 'applestore', 'United States', 'MOST FRUSTRATING APP EVER!!!', 'Waze was once my favorite app, with its innovative fusion between a road atlas and social media. But little things started to annoy me and grew worse and more frustrating over time!\nYour favorites can be arranged in whatever order you like, but then they will voluntarily move on their own, sorting themselves into random chaos by the time you\'ve opened the app again. I have many favorites and the miscellaneous sorting makes it VERY difficult to find an address quickly. Since Waze has never fixed this problem, it\'s obvious they don\'t really care.\nBut then came the bombshell!!! I was one of the first Wazers ever when the app was newly released, and for years I carefully reported road hazards, drove out of my way to pave new roads, and started adding business info in my community. I ascended to the highest Waze ranking in my state!!! I was on top of the world!!! And then I got a new phone...\nMy Waze profile was wiped out, my rank not even in the Top 50,000, and Waze said there was \"nothing they could do.\" Are you kidding me??? This is how you treat your most loyal customer??? My other 257 apps survived the new phone transfer flawlessly. Not Waze! Thanks for nothing Waze!!!', '332131159', 'applestore', 'France', 'Very good', 'Very good GPS I practically do not use the original one of my vehicle yet it is very recent', 'Waze', 0.0942943, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 414, -1, 2, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
