('211406383', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Navigation awful. Only good to see live conditions.', 'Navigation is downright awful due to map errors. And you can\'t edit most things yourself because you need to be one of the elite map editors. My reports never get fixed. So use Google Maps for navigation since it\'s faster and much more accurate. Use this app just to check traffic conditions. \n\nThe map constantly reverts to your current position after about 7 seconds if you pan away to look at traffic conditions. After weeks of back and forth with Waze, it\'s by design. How stupid is that?  If I\'m panning away, I want to be able to see what I\'ve panned to longer than 7 seconds without having it auto home. Until this gets resolved, it\'s one star for me.', '142655187', 'applestore', 'France', 'The best GPS application on the market!', 'How to skip this app !! After studying several applications, I am delighted with this one. Connected to my calendar, I am warned of my rdv so no need to return the address of my destination. Waze is a very intuitive, fast and efficient way to manage my time by programming my future departure, sharing my location to find friends. And what a pleasure to know that the new roads that have just opened are already recorded. How ??? Thanks to nature. .... bein yeah, it\'s gonna smile qlq one but that\'s the truth. Long live biomimicry !! Indeed, it is by studying nature that waze is able to differentiate from the competition. By studying the ants, and understanding how they were doing to convey information about the new galleries they were digging. Hence the great strength of this application. In this case bravo. I\'m a lot on the road and almost never late, among other things thanks to the performance of this application ?????.', 'Waze', 0.201977, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 434, -2, 2, 0.5, 'ot', 'ot'),
