('38515990', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Waze privacy is very poor', 'I used Waze for 4 years, but have stopped now, and deleted the app. \n\nThe crowd-sourcing of traffic conditions, hazards, sped traps was a great idea\n\nHowever, a major negative is that the app now requires you to share your entire contacts list in order to register. Google appear to be trying to build Facebook via the backdoor with their newly acquired driving app. Once you have let Google move  this information about all the other people you know to their servers you can\'t get it back. \n\nThe other privacy negative is that the Waze location tracking is required to be always on, rather than only on when app is on. This means that a breadcrumb of your every movement whether you are using Waze or not, whether you are in the car or on foot, is stored in Google\'s servers. There is no way to limit this unless you turn location services off - which of course disables the navigation in the app. \n\nWaze/Google need to reevaluate their privacy model for this app. It currently asks to know too much additional information about you, and this cannot be selectively turned off. I would suggest deleting this app on iOS devices until this policy is changed.', '85335716', 'applestore', 'France', 'Some shortcomings', 'Always essential for the Ile-de-France traffic, I use it daily. Two important shortcomings all the same: - The updates follow one another, but the vertical bar of the radar zone on the left and that of the sharing of the route on the right are still not visible in landscape mode ... Is there a reason for this incomprehensible lack? ? - Compatibility CarPlay, although Apple may be more to blame for this, we do not feel that Google is pushing too hard either to integrate it ... Too bad, Waze is infinitely more effective than Plan.', 'Waze', 0.21022, 1, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 544, 0, -1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('38634759', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Cannot plan future drive', 'All of a sudden the app is not letting me plan a ride for later in the day or following days. Won\'t load traffic expectations or the planned arrival time', '456226732', 'applestore', 'France', 'Why pay more?', 'Nice, practical, and amply enough for a small wheeler like me.', 'Waze', 0.0267362, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 545, 0, 1, 0.875, 'br', 'ot'),
