('422368615', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Location Services Always On', 'Waze keeps draining my battery and getting my location so Google can use my location to bother me with advertising.\n\nIt\'s annoying having to go to Settings and move Waze location services to NEVER when closing the app. CHANGE IT TO ONLY WHEN USING (location services).', '78034301', 'applestore', 'France', 'Permanent Location &amp; Big Battery Console', 'Even when the application is turned off Waze uses your location data. No possibility to activate the location in mode &quot;when the app is active&quot;. So locating and exchanging permanent data: it eats the battery and I do not want to be tracked down.', 'Waze', 0.248292, 3, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 571, -2, 0, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
