('42569937', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Not happy', 'Waze just would not let me use my account on my new phone. It said it recognized my number and showed my account. It needed to access my contacts to verify my account then said \"your account is lost somewhere in our stratosphere\" and would not let me use it. The minimal customer service they have did not let me speak to someone about this. I was a top 10% user in my state too. \nI\'m also not happy that waze uses my location while not in the app. That is unnecessary', '47670312', 'applestore', 'France', 'Le must have ! Mais...', 'Let\'s be honest !, who do not use Waze these days, almost people. I do not have too much negative side to say even if I\'m really disappointed because I was abroad and I go back at least twice a year and I had to carefully save favorites with places and Nice restaurants, not to mention the useful addresses of friends, since the update iOS 10 and impossible to recover my favorites it made me all shoot! I\'m just disgusting! 3 months of travel and registration of addresses that I would not find again! Too bad that waze does not think of making a cloud option or synchronization with iCloud for example', 'Waze', 0.205066, 2, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 576, -1, -2, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
