('6637723', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Latests Update not routing properly', 'i have noticed that since the last update the routing or rerouting function is not taking place making the functionality of the app diminished.  Maybe the servers cant handle all the queries from all the users or preferences that are avaialable to individuals isnt being stored.  I have access and use an employee only gate to get to my work destination.  Every morning now the route doesn\'t include access to the gate until i go past the turn it want me to take and then picks up to use the access restricted gate I use every day.  Frustrating and thats why stars are dropping.', '237837730', 'applestore', 'France', 'Perfect', 'Super practical in all circumstances, very useful for the problems of corks, saves me precious time by making me go through another way. Road hazards well reported but the community should differentiate between radar control and alcohol control and should report it.', 'Waze', 0.0820856, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 664, -2, 1, 0.625, 'br', 'br'),
