('87652731', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Always tracking', 'I\'ve used waze for 4 years now. I\'ve enjoyed every update and use the app every day. \n\nIn a recent update waze now demands that I either allow it to always track my location or never track my location. You used to be able to allow it to track only when the app was on (when I\'m driving). This is killing my battery life on an iPhone 6S.\n\nPLEASE FIX!!!\nTrust me, this app is always on when I am driving. I don\'t want it tracking gps info when I\'m sitting at work.', '144208991', 'applestore', 'France', 'Super', 'Indispensable for optimized journeys Highly integrated with car play', 'Waze', 0.00708541, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 676, 1, 2, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot');
